    <item>
      <title>自2022年以来，大多数人都会下降，因为交易员会付出更多的痛苦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统（Donald Trump）的全面贸易关税引发了美国货币的广泛撤退之后两年半以来，美元沉没，使商人努力进一步下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的贸易战在增长冲击方面袭击了欧洲股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布了一个世纪以来对贸易伙伴的最陡峭的美国关税之后，欧洲股票跌落，其中包括欧盟的20％的税率，这可能会削弱集团的暂定经济复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易者下注更多的美联储削减，为期10年的收益率向4％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-10-year-yield-drops-toward-4-as-tariffs-fuel-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易战将对美国经济产生适得其反的关注，债券交易者已取消了对美联储削减利率的押注，这将基准国库的收益率转移到了密切观看的4％水平上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-10-year-yield-drops-toward-4-as-tariffs-fuel-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普启动关税时，比特币屈服于资产低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/bitcoin-settles-in-narrow-range-after-trump-sets-trade-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统对全球贸易伙伴征收关税之后，比特币和其他重大加密货币下跌，引发了风险资产的低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/bitcoin-settles-in-narrow-range-after-trump-sets-trade-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:20:34 GMT</pubDate>
